{"id": "ChIJm4e5Q8rDwoARCrxRgEgqxd0", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 222, "displayName": {"text": "Delight Pastry", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJm4e5Q8rDwoARCrxRgEgqxd0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psMFFtbDJiMlF3WVhScFRDMVBTV2hxVmt4WlQzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Happy 5 years to Delight Pastry🎂✨\nWe finally tried their viral fruit desserts and now I totally get the hype🍓🥭 The strawberry + mango were so fresh, light, and refreshing.\n\nBut honestly… this place is dangerous because EVERYTHING looks good😍 From buttery croissants and fruit tarts to cakes, macarons, gelato, and even their lunch menu👀 We tried the Caprese Sandwich and it was the perfect savory break between all the sweets🥪✨\n\nDefinitely one of those Pasadena spots you walk into “just to look” and somehow leave with a full box of pastries🥰", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Happy 5 years to Delight Pastry🎂✨\nWe finally tried their viral fruit desserts and now I totally get the hype🍓🥭 The strawberry + mango were so fresh, light, and refreshing.\n\nBut honestly… this place is dangerous because EVERYTHING looks good😍 From buttery croissants and fruit tarts to cakes, macarons, gelato, and even their lunch menu👀 We tried the Caprese Sandwich and it was the perfect savory break between all the sweets🥪✨\n\nDefinitely one of those Pasadena spots you walk into “just to look” and somehow leave with a full box of pastries🥰", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Diana Chang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100719097444748903336/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdPmISZXJfHHbIVISj2QiZvM3U6d5k1JDboIkOAbKR3XgZ4Vk-3Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-13T02:40:44.482329498Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psMFFtbDJiMlF3WVhScFRDMVBTV2hxVmt4WlQzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psMFFtbDJiMlF3WVhScFRDMVBTV2hxVmt4WlQzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3ca43b9879b:0xddc52a488051bc0a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJm4e5Q8rDwoARCrxRgEgqxd0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214QlF6Uldia3Q0WkdaNE5uaE1jRkF3WTAxdkxWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The mango pastry is life changing, just the facts! The chocolate croissant was also amazing. The staff were super nice to me and my buddy Frank(dog)!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The mango pastry is life changing, just the facts! The chocolate croissant was also amazing. The staff were super nice to me and my buddy Frank(dog)!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Robert Jackson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110473741936681914611/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX98z_lx2adq0zo-crFlsG5r6P__Sd5xNY8-f6KolxhoiANf_zXlg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-01T23:38:33.617139867Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214QlF6Uldia3Q0WkdaNE5uaE1jRkF3WTAxdkxWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214QlF6Uldia3Q0WkdaNE5uaE1jRkF3WTAxdkxWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3ca43b9879b:0xddc52a488051bc0a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJm4e5Q8rDwoARCrxRgEgqxd0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5WVpVMVZSRlJzVWtSRFNUQmpOSFpwZWxkc1VYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Amazing. What a lovely pastry shop. Their coffee drinks are amazing too. So yummy - a MUST TRY in Pasadena! Service, food, everything is five stars ⭐️", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Amazing. What a lovely pastry shop. Their coffee drinks are amazing too. So yummy - a MUST TRY in Pasadena! Service, food, everything is five stars ⭐️", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Vincent Lussenburg", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110186728143755503418/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJoVMHD1WwjXYyNGST6tGjHYHn1u1ts9plqj_Mep9tX6W75JF0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-15T16:16:52.191369079Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5WVpVMVZSRlJzVWtSRFNUQmpOSFpwZWxkc1VYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5WVpVMVZSRlJzVWtSRFNUQmpOSFpwZWxkc1VYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3ca43b9879b:0xddc52a488051bc0a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJm4e5Q8rDwoARCrxRgEgqxd0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21saFNETlpOalZSU0dkUFF6UXROMlZzVmpoSllWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Yesterday was my second time coming in! The pastries are delicious and I love the variety, but yesterday I found what looked like a bristle from a kitchen scrub brush in my Kouign-amann! I was thoroughly enjoying my pastry, when I felt something like plastic in my mouth. At first it looked like a hair, but it’s definitely plastic. I believe this was probably a mistake, but I think they should aim to be a bit more careful with this. Again, the pastries did taste great though. I’d still return for more.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Yesterday was my second time coming in! The pastries are delicious and I love the variety, but yesterday I found what looked like a bristle from a kitchen scrub brush in my Kouign-amann! I was thoroughly enjoying my pastry, when I felt something like plastic in my mouth. At first it looked like a hair, but it’s definitely plastic. I believe this was probably a mistake, but I think they should aim to be a bit more careful with this. Again, the pastries did taste great though. I’d still return for more.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "David R", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102746919312530023811/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZtvaDYYKDPRikfOn2WMLcVr_VhGooMByz4q9IYLKii3EnO5r9_w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-22T18:34:21.401270738Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21saFNETlpOalZSU0dkUFF6UXROMlZzVmpoSllWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21saFNETlpOalZSU0dkUFF6UXROMlZzVmpoSllWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3ca43b9879b:0xddc52a488051bc0a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJm4e5Q8rDwoARCrxRgEgqxd0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sMFJXdHNURWRtUm1kVFNWUkxhMVJ6ZFRkWmRWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I didn’t even get a chance to take a proper picture before we started eating. 😅 Everything looked amazing, tasted even better, and disappeared within minutes. Definitely a sign of a great bakery!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I didn’t even get a chance to take a proper picture before we started eating. 😅 Everything looked amazing, tasted even better, and disappeared within minutes. Definitely a sign of a great bakery!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tatiana Kuzmyna", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104833844186719261736/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxhgkkuL0P1kQSrkq7VwmITXcdEYwOtnkeIHSEgELcLMAGquYS=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-02T20:09:11.411748563Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sMFJXdHNURWRtUm1kVFNWUkxhMVJ6ZFRkWmRWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sMFJXdHNURWRtU